cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with image segmentation using deep neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of conditional random fields for refinement is also a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper specifically deals with confocal microscopy images, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the use of deep neural networks for segmentation is a common application of neural networks (cs.NE).
